This is a tool for planning competitive pokemon sets written in c++ and using ncurses. It allows you to calculate the individual statistics of pokemon under item and nature modifiers. 

**It's a work in progress.**

#########
COMMANDS#
#########

To use the program you pass command strings, for example "mi131" or "me2252". You begin the command string with a command, and append it's arguments sans spaces.

q <quit>

m <modify the>
  + i <IV of the stat>
    + 1-6 <1=hp,2=att,6=hp>
	  + 0-31 <to this value>

  + e EV of the stat
    + 1-6 (1=hp,2=att,6=hp)
	  + 0-252 <to this value>
